arts.ttl: Cheltenham Town prospect Freddy Willcox joins Oxford City on loan
arts.sum: Cheltenham Town midfielder Freddy Willcox has joined National League North club Oxford City on loan until the end of the season. “It feels really good to be here," he said after signing for City .

arts.ttl: Cheltenham Town v Salford City RECAP: Bristol City loanee Tommy Backwell and Jordan Thomas on target in home win
arts.sum: Cheltenham Town: Day; Jude-Boyd (Power 90+1), Stubbs, Bennett, Bradbury; Kinsella, L Young; Thomas (Bakare 90+1) Backwell (Hay 72), Archer; Miller (M Taylor 62). Salford captain Curtis Tilt's header from Liam Shephard's corner crossed the line in the final seconds, but Cheltenham had done enough to end a run of three league games without a win.

arts.ttl: Tommy Backwell and Jordan Thomas give Cheltenham win against Salford
arts.sum: Thomas’ first Whaddon Road goal 10 minutes from the end condemned Salford to their second successive defeat.

arts.ttl: Cheltenham Town midfielder joins Wealdstone on loan
arts.sum: Boss Michael Flynn has regularly spoken about the Gloucester-born left-footer's technical prowess, but believes he needs to work on his all-round game before he is ready for regular League Two football. Cheltenham Town midfielder Harrison Sohna has joined National League club Wealdstone on loan until the end of the season.
